block helpModal
	#helpModal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-labelledby='myModalLabel')
		.modal-dialog(role='document')
			.modal-content
				.modal-header
					button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal', aria-label='Close')
						span(aria-hidden='true') ×
					h4#myModalLabel.modal-title Help
				.modal-body
					a.btn.btn-primary(role='button', data-toggle='collapse', href='#explanation1') How do I play?
					#explanation1.collapse
						.well
							| Underline the green text to win.  Use shorter regex and be speedy for a higher score
					a.btn.btn-primary(role='button', data-toggle='collapse', href='#explanation2') What is Regex?
					#explanation2.collapse
						.well Regex is a way of matching text.  Think of it as a text-search on steroids.  You can read more about it at https://regexone.com
					a.btn.btn-primary(role='button', data-toggle='collapse', href='#explanation3') What are these flags?
					#explanation3.collapse
						.well
							| * m: multiline (anchors apply to each line)
							br
							|		 * i: case-insensitive
							br
							|		 * g: global
							br
							|		 * javascript does not have any other flags
				.modal-footer
					button.btn.btn-default(type='button', data-dismiss='modal') Close
